# Python TUI

Keep Textual UI code focused on presentation and interaction.

## Rules

- Keep business logic outside Textual widgets.
- Keep widgets small and named by user-facing purpose.
- Test application construction without requiring a live terminal session.
- Avoid live network or model calls from UI tests.
- Use Rich/Textual components before custom terminal control code.

## Commands

```bash
make test
uv run pytest tests/unit/test_smoke.py
uv run {{ project_slug }}
```
